This paper deals with hate speech detection on social media, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves collecting and analyzing data, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). The paper also deals with reliability and accuracy, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
